    {"id":"c_s1_t","type":"text","x":1465,"y":355,"width":1530,"height":266,"angle":0,"strokeColor":"#0c4a6e","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"groupIds":[],"roundness":null,"seed":101,"version":1,"versionNonce":101,"isDeleted":false,"boundElements":[],"updated":1746400000000,"index":"aZ","link":null,"locked":false,"frameId":null,"text":"Step 1 вЂ” READ  (understand ALL constraints before touching code)\nв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓ\nв‘  Task row in TASKS.md вЂ” confirm ID, dependencies, spec_ref, AC reference\nв‘Ў Spec file for this domain (Spec1=Auth, Spec2=Products, Spec4=Orders, Spec5=Payment, Spec6=QR-POS, Spec7=Staff)\nв‘ў MASTER_v1.2.md вЂ” ONLY the sections that apply to this task:\n     В§2 design tokens в†’ any UI     В§3 RBAC в†’ any auth/roles     В§4 biz rules в†’ orders/payment/cancel     В§5 realtime в†’ SSE/WS     В§6 JWT в†’ auth\nв‘Ј BanhCuon_DB_SCHEMA_SUMMARY.md вЂ” verify EVERY field name before writing query or struct\nв‘¤ ERROR_CONTRACT_v1.1.md вЂ” verify error code before writing any error response\nв‘Ґ API_CONTRACT_v1.2.md вЂ” verify endpoint signature before writing handler\n\nRed flags в†’ stop now:\n  Spec section missing or 'TBD' в†’ вќ“ CLARIFY В· Two docs contradict в†’ вљ пёЏ FLAG В· Dep unresolved в†’ рџ”ґ STOP","fontSize":12,"fontFamily":2,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","containerId":null,"originalText":"Step 1 вЂ” READ  (understand ALL constraints before touching code)\nв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓ\nв‘  Task row in TASKS.md вЂ” confirm ID, dependencies, spec_ref, AC reference\nв‘Ў Spec file for this domain (Spec1=Auth, Spec2=Products, Spec4=Orders, Spec5=Payment, Spec6=QR-POS, Spec7=Staff)\nв‘ў MASTER_v1.2.md вЂ” ONLY the sections that apply to this task:\n     В§2 design tokens в†’ any UI     В§3 RBAC в†’ any auth/roles     В§4 biz rules в†’ orders/payment/cancel     В§5 realtime в†’ SSE/WS     В§6 JWT в†’ auth\nв‘Ј BanhCuon_DB_SCHEMA_SUMMARY.md вЂ” verify EVERY field name before writing query or struct\nв‘¤ ERROR_CONTRACT_v1.1.md вЂ” verify error code before writing any error response\nв‘Ґ API_CONTRACT_v1.2.md вЂ” verify endpoint signature before writing handler\n\nRed flags в†’ stop now:\n  Spec section missing or 'TBD' в†’ вќ“ CLARIFY В· Two docs contradict в†’ вљ пёЏ FLAG В· Dep unresolved в†’ рџ”ґ STOP","lineHeight":1.35,"autoResize":false},

