    {"id":"c_s2_t","type":"text","x":1465,"y":663,"width":1530,"height":141,"angle":0,"strokeColor":"#14532d","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"groupIds":[],"roundness":null,"seed":103,"version":1,"versionNonce":103,"isDeleted":false,"boundElements":[],"updated":1746400000000,"index":"b2","link":null,"locked":false,"frameId":null,"text":"Step 2 вЂ” PLAN  (write plan before a single line of code)\nв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓ\nFiles to CREATE: [list with full paths]     Files to MODIFY: [list + what changes]\nApproach: step-by-step logic for main function В· how it connects to adjacent layers\nRisks / Questions: ambiguity, edge cases, security concerns\nDeps checked: confirm prior tasks are вњ… in TASKS.md\nNote: payments + auth в†’ explicit caution flag В· multi-table write в†’ plan a transaction\nNote: new DB query needed в†’ add 'write query to query/*.sql' as first sub-step","fontSize":12,"fontFamily":2,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","containerId":null,"originalText":"Step 2 вЂ” PLAN  (write plan before a single line of code)\nв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓ\nFiles to CREATE: [list with full paths]     Files to MODIFY: [list + what changes]\nApproach: step-by-step logic for main function В· how it connects to adjacent layers\nRisks / Questions: ambiguity, edge cases, security concerns\nDeps checked: confirm prior tasks are вњ… in TASKS.md\nNote: payments + auth в†’ explicit caution flag В· multi-table write в†’ plan a transaction\nNote: new DB query needed в†’ add 'write query to query/*.sql' as first sub-step","lineHeight":1.35,"autoResize":false},

