    {"id":"c_s3_t","type":"text","x":1465,"y":846,"width":1530,"height":121,"angle":0,"strokeColor":"#713f12","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"groupIds":[],"roundness":null,"seed":105,"version":1,"versionNonce":105,"isDeleted":false,"boundElements":[],"updated":1746400000000,"index":"b5","link":null,"locked":false,"frameId":null,"text":"Step 3 вЂ” ALIGN  (confirm with user BEFORE writing code)\nв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓ\nALWAYS ask if: task is security-sensitive (auth, payments, webhook, RBAC) В· plan deviates from spec\n              open risk from Step 2 В· spec is ambiguous on edge case that affects implementation\nCan skip if:  plan is straightforward В· no spec ambiguity В· no security concern В· no open risk\nSignal is ambiguity + security risk вЂ” NOT line count or file count alone","fontSize":12,"fontFamily":2,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","containerId":null,"originalText":"Step 3 вЂ” ALIGN  (confirm with user BEFORE writing code)\nв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓ\nALWAYS ask if: task is security-sensitive (auth, payments, webhook, RBAC) В· plan deviates from spec\n              open risk from Step 2 В· spec is ambiguous on edge case that affects implementation\nCan skip if:  plan is straightforward В· no spec ambiguity В· no security concern В· no open risk\nSignal is ambiguity + security risk вЂ” NOT line count or file count alone","lineHeight":1.35,"autoResize":false},

    {"id":"c_arr34","type":"arrow","x":2230,"y":978,"width":0,"height":20,"angle":0,"strokeColor":"#475569","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"groupIds":[],"roundness":{"type":2},"seed":112,"version":1,"versionNonce":112,"isDeleted":false,"boundElements":[],"updated":1746400000000,"index":"b6","link":null,"locked":false,"frameId":null,"points":[[0,0],[0,20]],"lastCommittedPoint":null,"startBinding":null,"endBinding":null,"startArrowhead":null,"endArrowhead":"arrow"},

    {"id":"c_s4_r","type":"rectangle","x":1450,"y":1002,"width":1560,"height":305,"angle":0,"strokeColor":"#ea580c","backgroundColor":"#fff7ed","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"groupIds":[],"roundness":{"type":3},"seed":106,"version":1,"versionNonce":106,"isDeleted":false,"boundElements":[],"updated":1746400000000,"index":"b7","link":null,"locked":false,"frameId":null},
    {"id":"c_s4_t","type":"text","x":1465,"y":1009,"width":1530,"height":291,"angle":0,"strokeColor":"#7c2d12","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"groupIds":[],"roundness":null,"seed":107,"version":1,"versionNonce":107,"isDeleted":false,"boundElements":[],"updated":1746400000000,"index":"b8","link":null,"locked":false,"frameId":null,"text":"Step 4 вЂ” IMPLEMENT  (code exactly as planned, no additions)\nв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓ\nBE strict layer order (no exceptions): handler в†’ service в†’ repository в†’ db (sqlc-generated)\n  handler:    gin.Context В· bind JSON В· call service В· return response (NO business logic)\n  service:    business logic В· state machine В· error mapping (NO gin imports В· NO direct DB)\n  repository: sqlc wrappers В· transaction helpers (NO business rules)\n  db/:        sqlc-generated вЂ” NEVER edit manually\n  Rules: all IDs = string(UUID CHAR36) В· all errors = respondError() В· Redis = always set TTL\n         multi-table mutations = use transaction В· auth before RBAC middleware\n         Webhook: HMAC verification is FIRST operation before reading ANY body field\n\nFE state ownership (no exceptions):\n  Server data (products/orders) в†’ TanStack Query useQuery\n  Auth token / cart             в†’ Zustand store (NEVER localStorage, NEVER sessionStorage)\n  Form data                     в†’ React Hook Form + Zod\n  API calls                     в†’ api-client.ts ONLY (never raw fetch or direct axios)\n  Colors                        в†’ Tailwind token names (NEVER hex in className)\n  Price display                 в†’ formatVND() from lib/utils.ts (ALWAYS)","fontSize":12,"fontFamily":2,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","containerId":null,"originalText":"Step 4 вЂ” IMPLEMENT  (code exactly as planned, no additions)\nв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓ\nBE strict layer order (no exceptions): handler в†’ service в†’ repository в†’ db (sqlc-generated)\n  handler:    gin.Context В· bind JSON В· call service В· return response (NO business logic)\n  service:    business logic В· state machine В· error mapping (NO gin imports В· NO direct DB)\n  repository: sqlc wrappers В· transaction helpers (NO business rules)\n  db/:        sqlc-generated вЂ” NEVER edit manually\n  Rules: all IDs = string(UUID CHAR36) В· all errors = respondError() В· Redis = always set TTL\n         multi-table mutations = use transaction В· auth before RBAC middleware\n         Webhook: HMAC verification is FIRST operation before reading ANY body field\n\nFE state ownership (no exceptions):\n  Server data (products/orders) в†’ TanStack Query useQuery\n  Auth token / cart             в†’ Zustand store (NEVER localStorage, NEVER sessionStorage)\n  Form data                     в†’ React Hook Form + Zod\n  API calls                     в†’ api-client.ts ONLY (never raw fetch or direct axios)\n  Colors                        в†’ Tailwind token names (NEVER hex in className)\n  Price display                 в†’ formatVND() from lib/utils.ts (ALWAYS)","lineHeight":1.35,"autoResize":false},

    {"id":"c_arr45","type":"arrow","x":2230,"y":1311,"width":0,"height":20,"angle":0,"strokeColor":"#475569","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"groupIds":[],"roundness":{"type":2},"seed":113,"version":1,"versionNonce":113,"isDeleted":false,"boundElements":[],"updated":1746400000000,"index":"b9","link":null,"locked":false,"frameId":null,"points":[[0,0],[0,20]],"lastCommittedPoint":null,"startBinding":null,"endBinding":null,"startArrowhead":null,"endArrowhead":"arrow"},

    {"id":"c_s5_r","type":"rectangle","x":1450,"y":1335,"width":1560,"height":295,"angle":0,"strokeColor":"#9d174d","backgroundColor":"#fdf2f8","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"groupIds":[],"roundness":{"type":3},"seed":108,"version":1,"versionNonce":108,"isDeleted":false,"boundElements":[],"updated":1746400000000,"index":"bA","link":null,"locked":false,"frameId":null},
    {"id":"c_s5_t","type":"text","x":1465,"y":1342,"width":1530,"height":281,"angle":0,"strokeColor":"#500724","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"groupIds":[],"roundness":null,"seed":109,"version":1,"versionNonce":109,"isDeleted":false,"boundElements":[],"updated":1746400000000,"index":"bB","link":null,"locked":false,"frameId":null,"text":"Step 5 вЂ” SELF-REVIEW  (audit the code before presenting вЂ” treat as mandatory)\nв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓ\nSecurity:\n  в–Ў JWT: verify t.Method == jwt.SigningMethodHMAC before parsing\n  в–Ў No username enumeration (wrong pw = exact same error as wrong username)\n  в–Ў Webhook: HMAC verified BEFORE any DB read or write\n  в–Ў No SQL injection (sqlc parameterized queries only вЂ” no string concat)\n  в–Ў No sensitive data in logs (passwords, tokens, gateway keys)\n  в–Ў CORS origins from env var, not hardcoded\n\nCorrectness:\n  в–Ў Happy path matches spec В· all errors use correct code from ERROR_CONTRACT\n  в–Ў State machine transitions validated (no skipping states)\n  в–Ў 1-table-1-active-order check before CreateOrder\n  в–Ў Payment idempotency: check existing status before updating\n  в–Ў recalculateTotalAmount() called after EVERY order_items mutation\n  в–Ў Soft delete: deleted_at set, NOT hard DELETE В· all queries filter WHERE deleted_at IS NULL\n\nFrontend:\n  в–Ў No token in localStorage В· no hardcoded hex colors В· all IDs typed as string\n  в–Ў SSE: Bearer header В· WS: query param (browser limitation, cannot set custom WS headers)","fontSize":12,"fontFamily":2,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","containerId":null,"originalText":"Step 5 вЂ” SELF-REVIEW  (audit the code before presenting вЂ” treat as mandatory)\nв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓ\nSecurity:\n  в–Ў JWT: verify t.Method == jwt.SigningMethodHMAC before parsing\n  в–Ў No username enumeration (wrong pw = exact same error as wrong username)\n  в–Ў Webhook: HMAC verified BEFORE any DB read or write\n  в–Ў No SQL injection (sqlc parameterized queries only вЂ” no string concat)\n  в–Ў No sensitive data in logs (passwords, tokens, gateway keys)\n  в–Ў CORS origins from env var, not hardcoded\n\nCorrectness:\n  в–Ў Happy path matches spec В· all errors use correct code from ERROR_CONTRACT\n  в–Ў State machine transitions validated (no skipping states)\n  в–Ў 1-table-1-active-order check before CreateOrder\n  в–Ў Payment idempotency: check existing status before updating\n  в–Ў recalculateTotalAmount() called after EVERY order_items mutation\n  в–Ў Soft delete: deleted_at set, NOT hard DELETE В· all queries filter WHERE deleted_at IS NULL\n\nFrontend:\n  в–Ў No token in localStorage В· no hardcoded hex colors В· all IDs typed as string\n  в–Ў SSE: Bearer header В· WS: query param (browser limitation, cannot set custom WS headers)","lineHeight":1.35,"autoResize":false},

