    {"id":"c_s6_t","type":"text","x":1465,"y":1665,"width":1530,"height":156,"angle":0,"strokeColor":"#14532d","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"groupIds":[],"roundness":null,"seed":116,"version":1,"versionNonce":116,"isDeleted":false,"boundElements":[],"updated":1746400000000,"index":"bE","link":null,"locked":false,"frameId":null,"text":"Step 6 вЂ” TEST  (verify before marking done)\nв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓ\nBE service: go build ./...  (zero errors) + unit test main logic path\nFE component: npm run build  (zero TS errors) + check in browser + console errors\nDB query: sqlc generate  (no errors) + verify generated types match schema\nDevOps: docker compose up -d --build [service]  в†’ container starts + passes health check\n\nAuth tasks: test wrong pw = wrong user SAME error В· rate limit after 5 fails\nPayment tasks: test HMAC rejection В· test idempotency (call webhook twice)\nOrder tasks: test 1-table-1-active check В· test state machine rejects invalid transition\nIf tests cannot run в†’ state explicitly + list the exact commands to run later","fontSize":12,"fontFamily":2,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","containerId":null,"originalText":"Step 6 вЂ” TEST  (verify before marking done)\nв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓ\nBE service: go build ./...  (zero errors) + unit test main logic path\nFE component: npm run build  (zero TS errors) + check in browser + console errors\nDB query: sqlc generate  (no errors) + verify generated types match schema\nDevOps: docker compose up -d --build [service]  в†’ container starts + passes health check\n\nAuth tasks: test wrong pw = wrong user SAME error В· rate limit after 5 fails\nPayment tasks: test HMAC rejection В· test idempotency (call webhook twice)\nOrder tasks: test 1-table-1-active check В· test state machine rejects invalid transition\nIf tests cannot run в†’ state explicitly + list the exact commands to run later","lineHeight":1.35,"autoResize":false},

