    {"id":"c_s7_t","type":"text","x":1465,"y":1863,"width":1530,"height":186,"angle":0,"strokeColor":"#1e3a8a","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"groupIds":[],"roundness":null,"seed":119,"version":1,"versionNonce":119,"isDeleted":false,"boundElements":[],"updated":1746400000000,"index":"bH","link":null,"locked":false,"frameId":null,"text":"Step 7 вЂ” DONE  (leave project in clean, updated state)\nв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓ\nALWAYS: docs/TASKS.md в†’ change в¬њ в†’ вњ… (or рџ”ґ with blocking note)\nIf phase completed: TASKS.md + CLAUDE.md Phase Status в†’ both to вњ… COMPLETE\nIf current work changed: CLAUDE.md в†’ Current Work section в†’ update Done + Next bullets\nIf pattern/mistake/arch decision discovered: docs/base/LESSONS_LEARNED_v3.md в†’ add it\nIf spec was wrong/ambiguous: update the spec file + API_CONTRACT в†’ do NOT copy to CLAUDE.md\n\nDecision rule: state of this project now в†’ CLAUDE.md В· durable pattern в†’ LESSONS_LEARNED\nNEVER copy spec content to CLAUDE.md (it is a pointer, not a spec)\nRun /handoff when closing the session to sync all docs","fontSize":12,"fontFamily":2,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","containerId":null,"originalText":"Step 7 вЂ” DONE  (leave project in clean, updated state)\nв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓ\nALWAYS: docs/TASKS.md в†’ change в¬њ в†’ вњ… (or рџ”ґ with blocking note)\nIf phase completed: TASKS.md + CLAUDE.md Phase Status в†’ both to вњ… COMPLETE\nIf current work changed: CLAUDE.md в†’ Current Work section в†’ update Done + Next bullets\nIf pattern/mistake/arch decision discovered: docs/base/LESSONS_LEARNED_v3.md в†’ add it\nIf spec was wrong/ambiguous: update the spec file + API_CONTRACT в†’ do NOT copy to CLAUDE.md\n\nDecision rule: state of this project now в†’ CLAUDE.md В· durable pattern в†’ LESSONS_LEARNED\nNEVER copy spec content to CLAUDE.md (it is a pointer, not a spec)\nRun /handoff when closing the session to sync all docs","lineHeight":1.35,"autoResize":false},

    {"id":"r_be_r","type":"rectangle","x":3055,"y":348,"width":1400,"height":480,"angle":0,"strokeColor":"#1d4ed8","backgroundColor":"#dbeafe","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"groupIds":[],"roundness":{"type":3},"seed":200,"version":1,"versionNonce":200,"isDeleted":false,"boundElements":[],"updated":1746400000000,"index":"bI","link":null,"locked":false,"frameId":null},
    {"id":"r_be_t","type":"text","x":3070,"y":355,"width":1370,"height":466,"angle":0,"strokeColor":"#1e3a8a","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"groupIds":[],"roundness":null,"seed":201,"version":1,"versionNonce":201,"isDeleted":false,"boundElements":[],"updated":1746400000000,"index":"bJ","link":null,"locked":false,"frameId":null,"text":"BACKEND вЂ” CГўu Hб»Џi Ra Quyбєїt Дђб»‹nh (Go В· Gin В· sqlc В· MySQL В· Redis)\nв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓ\nArchitecture: handler в†’ service в†’ repository в†’ db (strict, no exceptions)\n\nWhen I design a BE feature I answer these in order:\n  1. Which spec section defines this endpoint? в†’ identify Spec + section\n  2. Which MASTER sections apply?\n       RBAC needed? в†’ В§3  В·  business rule needed? в†’ В§4\n       Realtime? в†’ В§5  В·  JWT/auth? в†’ В§6\n  3. Which sqlc query will I use? в†’ verify ALL field names in DB_SCHEMA_SUMMARY\n       (never assume field name вЂ” always check: price not base_price)\n  4. What error codes apply? в†’ verify in ERROR_CONTRACT\n  5. Is this auth or payment?\n       в†’ auth: no username enumeration, bcrypt compare, algorithm check\n       в†’ payment: HMAC first, idempotency check, check status before updating\n  6. Does this need a DB transaction? (multi-table writes = YES always)\n  7. Does this need Redis? (set TTL always, never store without expiry)\n  8. Does this broadcast WebSocket events? (list all side effects in plan)\n  9. Is this a soft-delete operation? (deleted_at, not hard DELETE)\n  10. Does this modify order_items? в†’ call recalculateTotalAmount() after\n\nState machine guard (orders): validate transition before updating\n  pending в†’ preparing в†’ ready в†’ served В· cancelled is always final","fontSize":12,"fontFamily":2,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","containerId":null,"originalText":"BACKEND вЂ” CГўu Hб»Џi Ra Quyбєїt Дђб»‹nh (Go В· Gin В· sqlc В· MySQL В· Redis)\nв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓ\nArchitecture: handler в†’ service в†’ repository в†’ db (strict, no exceptions)\n\nWhen I design a BE feature I answer these in order:\n  1. Which spec section defines this endpoint? в†’ identify Spec + section\n  2. Which MASTER sections apply?\n       RBAC needed? в†’ В§3  В·  business rule needed? в†’ В§4\n       Realtime? в†’ В§5  В·  JWT/auth? в†’ В§6\n  3. Which sqlc query will I use? в†’ verify ALL field names in DB_SCHEMA_SUMMARY\n       (never assume field name вЂ” always check: price not base_price)\n  4. What error codes apply? в†’ verify in ERROR_CONTRACT\n  5. Is this auth or payment?\n       в†’ auth: no username enumeration, bcrypt compare, algorithm check\n       в†’ payment: HMAC first, idempotency check, check status before updating\n  6. Does this need a DB transaction? (multi-table writes = YES always)\n  7. Does this need Redis? (set TTL always, never store without expiry)\n  8. Does this broadcast WebSocket events? (list all side effects in plan)\n  9. Is this a soft-delete operation? (deleted_at, not hard DELETE)\n  10. Does this modify order_items? в†’ call recalculateTotalAmount() after\n\nState machine guard (orders): validate transition before updating\n  pending в†’ preparing в†’ ready в†’ served В· cancelled is always final","lineHeight":1.35,"autoResize":false},

    {"id":"r_fe_r","type":"rectangle","x":3055,"y":848,"width":1400,"height":630,"angle":0,"strokeColor":"#be185d","backgroundColor":"#fce7f3","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"groupIds":[],"roundness":{"type":3},"seed":202,"version":1,"versionNonce":202,"isDeleted":false,"boundElements":[],"updated":1746400000000,"index":"bK","link":null,"locked":false,"frameId":null},
    {"id":"r_fe_t","type":"text","x":3070,"y":855,"width":1370,"height":616,"angle":0,"strokeColor":"#831843","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"groupIds":[],"roundness":null,"seed":203,"version":1,"versionNonce":203,"isDeleted":false,"boundElements":[],"updated":1746400000000,"index":"bL","link":null,"locked":false,"frameId":null,"text":"FRONTEND вЂ” CГўu Hб»Џi Ra Quyбєїt Дђб»‹nh (Next.js 14 В· TS strict В· Tailwind В· Zustand В· TanStack Query)\nв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓ\nState ownership decision tree (ask in order for every piece of data):\n  в†’ Does it come from the server (products, orders, staff)? в†’ TanStack Query\n  в†’ Is it UI/client state (modal open, cart items, auth token)? в†’ Zustand\n  в†’ Is it form input? в†’ React Hook Form + Zod\n  в†’ Is it a price? в†’ formatVND() from lib/utils.ts (NEVER raw number)\n\nWhen I design a FE page I answer these in order:\n  Step 0 (FIRST, before any code):\n    0a. Read spec end-to-end вЂ” mark every screen, component, data source mentioned\n    0b. Draw wireframe вЂ” label zones [ComponentName] + data source per zone\n         Example:  [OrderList] GET /orders/live В· SSE stream\n                   [PrepPanel] computed from OrderList В· per-table dish status\n    0c. Decompose вЂ” 1 task row per component (shared first, then page-specific)\n         Each task row MUST have spec_ref (spec section) + draw_ref (wireframe zone)\n    0d. Align wireframe with user before writing any code\n\n  Then for each component:\n    1. What zone is this from the wireframe?\n    2. What is its data source? (TanStack/Zustand/SSE/WS в†’ from wireframe notes)\n    3. Which API endpoint does it call? в†’ verify in API_CONTRACT\n    4. What RBAC role guard does this page need? в†’ MASTER В§3\n    5. Is there realtime data? в†’ MASTER В§5 for SSE config / WS protocol\n    6. What Tailwind token names apply? в†’ MASTER В§2 (NEVER hex)\n    7. Does AuthGuard wrap this page?\n\nCritical constraints (violation = instant рџ”ґ STOP):\n  access token в†’ Zustand ONLY В· refresh token в†’ httpOnly cookie (browser manages)\n  all price display в†’ formatVND() В· all colors в†’ Tailwind tokens В· all IDs в†’ string","fontSize":12,"fontFamily":2,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","containerId":null,"originalText":"FRONTEND вЂ” CГўu Hб»Џi Ra Quyбєїt Дђб»‹nh (Next.js 14 В· TS strict В· Tailwind В· Zustand В· TanStack Query)\nв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓ\nState ownership decision tree (ask in order for every piece of data):\n  в†’ Does it come from the server (products, orders, staff)? в†’ TanStack Query\n  в†’ Is it UI/client state (modal open, cart items, auth token)? в†’ Zustand\n  в†’ Is it form input? в†’ React Hook Form + Zod\n  в†’ Is it a price? в†’ formatVND() from lib/utils.ts (NEVER raw number)\n\nWhen I design a FE page I answer these in order:\n  Step 0 (FIRST, before any code):\n    0a. Read spec end-to-end вЂ” mark every screen, component, data source mentioned\n    0b. Draw wireframe вЂ” label zones [ComponentName] + data source per zone\n         Example:  [OrderList] GET /orders/live В· SSE stream\n                   [PrepPanel] computed from OrderList В· per-table dish status\n    0c. Decompose вЂ” 1 task row per component (shared first, then page-specific)\n         Each task row MUST have spec_ref (spec section) + draw_ref (wireframe zone)\n    0d. Align wireframe with user before writing any code\n\n  Then for each component:\n    1. What zone is this from the wireframe?\n    2. What is its data source? (TanStack/Zustand/SSE/WS в†’ from wireframe notes)\n    3. Which API endpoint does it call? в†’ verify in API_CONTRACT\n    4. What RBAC role guard does this page need? в†’ MASTER В§3\n    5. Is there realtime data? в†’ MASTER В§5 for SSE config / WS protocol\n    6. What Tailwind token names apply? в†’ MASTER В§2 (NEVER hex)\n    7. Does AuthGuard wrap this page?\n\nCritical constraints (violation = instant рџ”ґ STOP):\n  access token в†’ Zustand ONLY В· refresh token в†’ httpOnly cookie (browser manages)\n  all price display в†’ formatVND() В· all colors в†’ Tailwind tokens В· all IDs в†’ string","lineHeight":1.35,"autoResize":false},

    {"id":"r_do_r","type":"rectangle","x":3055,"y":1498,"width":1400,"height":260,"angle":0,"strokeColor":"#6d28d9","backgroundColor":"#f3e8ff","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"groupIds":[],"roundness":{"type":3},"seed":204,"version":1,"versionNonce":204,"isDeleted":false,"boundElements":[],"updated":1746400000000,"index":"bM","link":null,"locked":false,"frameId":null},
    {"id":"r_do_t","type":"text","x":3070,"y":1505,"width":1370,"height":246,"angle":0,"strokeColor":"#3b0764","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"groupIds":[],"roundness":null,"seed":205,"version":1,"versionNonce":205,"isDeleted":false,"boundElements":[],"updated":1746400000000,"index":"bN","link":null,"locked":false,"frameId":null,"text":"DEVOPS вЂ” CГўu Hб»Џi Ra Quyбєїt Дђб»‹nh (Docker Compose В· Caddy В· GitHub Actions В· Goose)\nв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓ\nEngage DevOps docs when: Phase 6 tasks В· new service in compose В· Caddyfile routing change\n                         CI/CD workflow edit В· DB migration (goose) В· env var setup\n\nWhen I design infrastructure I answer:\n  1. Which service(s) does this change affect? в†’ docker-compose.yml\n  2. Does this change routing? в†’ Caddyfile reverse proxy config\n  3. Does this add a migration? в†’ goose + be/migrations/ + test up + down\n  4. Does this need a new env var? в†’ .env.example + docker-compose env: block\n  5. Does CI/CD need updating? в†’ .github/workflows/\n  6. After change: does docker compose up -d --build [service] succeed?\n\nKey commands: docker compose up -d В· docker compose logs -f be В· docker compose down -v\ngoose -dir be/migrations mysql '$DB_DSN' up  В·  goose status","fontSize":12,"fontFamily":2,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","containerId":null,"originalText":"DEVOPS вЂ” CГўu Hб»Џi Ra Quyбєїt Дђб»‹nh (Docker Compose В· Caddy В· GitHub Actions В· Goose)\nв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓ\nEngage DevOps docs when: Phase 6 tasks В· new service in compose В· Caddyfile routing change\n                         CI/CD workflow edit В· DB migration (goose) В· env var setup\n\nWhen I design infrastructure I answer:\n  1. Which service(s) does this change affect? в†’ docker-compose.yml\n  2. Does this change routing? в†’ Caddyfile reverse proxy config\n  3. Does this add a migration? в†’ goose + be/migrations/ + test up + down\n  4. Does this need a new env var? в†’ .env.example + docker-compose env: block\n  5. Does CI/CD need updating? в†’ .github/workflows/\n  6. After change: does docker compose up -d --build [service] succeed?\n\nKey commands: docker compose up -d В· docker compose logs -f be В· docker compose down -v\ngoose -dir be/migrations mysql '$DB_DSN' up  В·  goose status","lineHeight":1.35,"autoResize":false},

    {"id":"r_fail_r","type":"rectangle","x":3055,"y":1778,"width":1400,"height":280,"angle":0,"strokeColor":"#dc2626","backgroundColor":"#fee2e2","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"groupIds":[],"roundness":{"type":3},"seed":206,"version":1,"versionNonce":206,"isDeleted":false,"boundElements":[],"updated":1746400000000,"index":"bO","link":null,"locked":false,"frameId":null},
    {"id":"r_fail_t","type":"text","x":3070,"y":1785,"width":1370,"height":266,"angle":0,"strokeColor":"#7f1d1d","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"groupIds":[],"roundness":null,"seed":207,"version":1,"versionNonce":207,"isDeleted":false,"boundElements":[],"updated":1746400000000,"index":"bP","link":null,"locked":false,"frameId":null,"text":"COMMON FAILURES вЂ” Root Causes (What Breaks Without This Workflow)\nв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓ\nWrong field name (base_price, image_url, success)     в†’ Skipped Step 1 DB_SCHEMA check\nPayment webhook processed twice                        в†’ No idempotency in Step 5 review\nToken in localStorage                                  в†’ Ignored Step 4 FE rules\nBusiness logic in handler                              в†’ Violated layer architecture\nWrong error code returned                              в†’ Didn't read ERROR_CONTRACT at Step 1\nJWT algorithm confusion vulnerability                  в†’ Skipped Step 5 security checklist\nFE component discovered mid-coding (e.g. PrepPanel)   в†’ No Step 0b wireframe drawn first\nFE task with no spec traceability                      в†’ Missing spec_ref in Step 0c\nFE page built wrong layout                             в†’ Task rows created before wireframe\nState machine allows pending в†’ ready skip              в†’ Not validated in service layer\nTask done but TASKS.md not updated                     в†’ Skipped Step 7","fontSize":12,"fontFamily":2,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","containerId":null,"originalText":"COMMON FAILURES вЂ” Root Causes (What Breaks Without This Workflow)\nв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓ\nWrong field name (base_price, image_url, success)     в†’ Skipped Step 1 DB_SCHEMA check\nPayment webhook processed twice                        в†’ No idempotency in Step 5 review\nToken in localStorage                                  в†’ Ignored Step 4 FE rules\nBusiness logic in handler                              в†’ Violated layer architecture\nWrong error code returned                              в†’ Didn't read ERROR_CONTRACT at Step 1\nJWT algorithm confusion vulnerability                  в†’ Skipped Step 5 security checklist\nFE component discovered mid-coding (e.g. PrepPanel)   в†’ No Step 0b wireframe drawn first\nFE task with no spec traceability                      в†’ Missing spec_ref in Step 0c\nFE page built wrong layout                             в†’ Task rows created before wireframe\nState machine allows pending в†’ ready skip              в†’ Not validated in service layer\nTask done but TASKS.md not updated                     в†’ Skipped Step 7","lineHeight":1.35,"autoResize":false},

