    {"id":"b_code_t","type":"text","x":2681,"y":2137,"width":530,"height":356,"angle":0,"strokeColor":"#14532d","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"groupIds":[],"roundness":null,"seed":391,"version":1,"versionNonce":391,"isDeleted":false,"boundElements":[],"updated":1746400000000,"index":"c9","link":null,"locked":false,"frameId":null,"text":"вњ… CODE вЂ” Delivered\nв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓ\nBE: handler В· service В· repository\nFE: page.tsx В· components В· api.ts\nDevOps: docker-compose В· Caddyfile\n\nVerified by:\n  go build ./... (zero errors)\n  npm run build (zero TS errors)\n  sqlc generate (no errors)\n  docker compose up --build\n\nDocs updated:\n  TASKS.md в†’ вњ…\n  CLAUDE.md в†’ Current Work\n  LESSONS_LEARNED (if pattern)\n\nBranch:\n  feature/<task-id>-<name>\n  PR в†’ merge в†’ delete branch","fontSize":12,"fontFamily":2,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","containerId":null,"originalText":"вњ… CODE вЂ” Delivered\nв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓ\nBE: handler В· service В· repository\nFE: page.tsx В· components В· api.ts\nDevOps: docker-compose В· Caddyfile\n\nVerified by:\n  go build ./... (zero errors)\n  npm run build (zero TS errors)\n  sqlc generate (no errors)\n  docker compose up --build\n\nDocs updated:\n  TASKS.md в†’ вњ…\n  CLAUDE.md в†’ Current Work\n  LESSONS_LEARNED (if pattern)\n\nBranch:\n  feature/<task-id>-<name>\n  PR в†’ merge в†’ delete branch","lineHeight":1.35,"autoResize":false},

    {"id":"b_notes_r","type":"rectangle","x":3280,"y":2130,"width":1170,"height":370,"angle":0,"strokeColor":"#475569","backgroundColor":"#f1f5f9","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"groupIds":[],"roundness":{"type":3},"seed":400,"version":1,"versionNonce":400,"isDeleted":false,"boundElements":[],"updated":1746400000000,"index":"cA","link":null,"locked":false,"frameId":null},
    {"id":"b_notes_t","type":"text","x":3295,"y":2137,"width":1140,"height":356,"angle":0,"strokeColor":"#1e293b","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"groupIds":[],"roundness":null,"seed":401,"version":1,"versionNonce":401,"isDeleted":false,"boundElements":[],"updated":1746400000000,"index":"cB","link":null,"locked":false,"frameId":null,"text":"KEY PRINCIPLES вЂ” Дђiб»Ѓu Quan Trб»Ќng NhбєҐt\nв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓ\n1. ONE FACT, ONE HOME\n   Every piece of information has exactly ONE authoritative source.\n   DB field names в†’ DB_SCHEMA_SUMMARY В· Endpoints в†’ API_CONTRACT В· Error codes в†’ ERROR_CONTRACT\n   Never duplicate facts across docs вЂ” only one doc changes when reality changes.\n\n2. READ BEFORE CODE (always)\n   I never code from memory. I verify field names, error codes, endpoint signatures\n   against the source docs EVERY time, even for fields I've used before.\n\n3. DOCS HAVE TIERS вЂ” only read what's needed for the current task\n   Tбє§ng 1: always В· Tбє§ng 2: only relevant sections В· Tбє§ng 3: only current domain\n   docs/qui_trinh/ = ORIGIN, never reference during coding\n\n4. FE WIREFRAME IS NOT OPTIONAL\n   Building a FE page without a wireframe = discovering layout problems mid-code.\n   Wireframe в†’ decompose в†’ task rows WITH spec_ref + draw_ref в†’ THEN code.\n\n5. TASKS.md IS THE SINGLE SOURCE OF TASK TRUTH\n   When CLAUDE.md and TASKS.md disagree в†’ TASKS.md wins. Always update TASKS.md\n   after every task. Status drift = confusion in next session.\n\n6. PREFIX SYSTEM IS HOW I COMMUNICATE RISK\n   рџ’Ў optional В· вљ пёЏ needs attention В· рџљЁ high risk В· рџ”ґ do not proceed В· вќ“ need answer В· рџ”„ pivot","fontSize":12,"fontFamily":2,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","containerId":null,"originalText":"KEY PRINCIPLES вЂ” Дђiб»Ѓu Quan Trб»Ќng NhбєҐt\nв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓ\n1. ONE FACT, ONE HOME\n   Every piece of information has exactly ONE authoritative source.\n   DB field names в†’ DB_SCHEMA_SUMMARY В· Endpoints в†’ API_CONTRACT В· Error codes в†’ ERROR_CONTRACT\n   Never duplicate facts across docs вЂ” only one doc changes when reality changes.\n\n2. READ BEFORE CODE (always)\n   I never code from memory. I verify field names, error codes, endpoint signatures\n   against the source docs EVERY time, even for fields I've used before.\n\n3. DOCS HAVE TIERS вЂ” only read what's needed for the current task\n   Tбє§ng 1: always В· Tбє§ng 2: only relevant sections В· Tбє§ng 3: only current domain\n   docs/qui_trinh/ = ORIGIN, never reference during coding\n\n4. FE WIREFRAME IS NOT OPTIONAL\n   Building a FE page without a wireframe = discovering layout problems mid-code.\n   Wireframe в†’ decompose в†’ task rows WITH spec_ref + draw_ref в†’ THEN code.\n\n5. TASKS.md IS THE SINGLE SOURCE OF TASK TRUTH\n   When CLAUDE.md and TASKS.md disagree в†’ TASKS.md wins. Always update TASKS.md\n   after every task. Status drift = confusion in next session.\n\n6. PREFIX SYSTEM IS HOW I COMMUNICATE RISK\n   рџ’Ў optional В· вљ пёЏ needs attention В· рџљЁ high risk В· рџ”ґ do not proceed В· вќ“ need answer В· рџ”„ pivot","lineHeight":1.35,"autoResize":false}

